metadata.name: Awakening
metadata.description: Year 2018. I opened my eyes to the world with my ice blue eyes, black and white patterns, aesthetic tail and pointed ears. Thousands of adventures await me yet to discover. I was excited but also nervous. Because in this place they call the world, I didn't know what was going on. Was everyone happy? Did they love the world? Or did they suddenly open their eyes to the world and try to get used to it, like me? I have only been on this planet for 2 months and I still have a hard time understanding whether people love this planet or not. They look happy when they're playing with me, but are they happy when they're not with me? For now, I'm trying to learn people's language. They call me Eddy. For most of the day, I fall asleep dreaming of my future adventures. Hear me! Maybe you will learn about you and this planet we live on for the first time from the mouth of my kind...
